PrecisOrder (a) withdrawing the powers, duties and functions conferred upon the Minister of Finance by Order in Council P.C. 1989-134 of January 30, 1989, with respect to the Office of Privatization and Regulatory Affairs; and (b) transferring the control and supervision of certain sectors of that Office to the Department of Finance and to the Treasury Board Secretariat.

precis:
Order (a) withdrawing the powers, duties and functions conferred upon the
Minister of Finance by Order in Council P.C. 1989-134 of January 30, 1989,
with respect to the Office of Privatization and Regulatory Affairs; and
(b) transferring the control and supervision of certain sectors of that
Office to the Department of Finance and to the Treasury Board Secretariat.
